headline: Kimberly-Clark: The Kenvue Deal Could Be Used To Cut The Dividend - Strong Sell
summary: Kimberly-Clark (KMB) stock faces risks from the $48.7B Kenvue acquisition, high debt, and weak growth. Learn why analysts rate it a strong sell.
